没关系，你不用忙
It's fine. You don't have to.

5
00:00:41,340 --> 00:00:42,800
我就叫你别动了
I told you not to move!

6
00:00:48,930 --> 00:00:50,440
你在做什么？
What are you doing?

7
00:00:50,940 --> 00:00:52,350
没有关系
It's fine.

8
00:00:52,440 --> 00:00:55,520
医生们只是爱担心才帮我用这些东西，其实我根本不需要
The doctors were just worried. I don't need all that.

9
00:00:55,610 --> 00:00:59,110
才不是，医生们学问好才会这么要求
The smart doctors know what they're doing. Listen to them.

10
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:02,990
往后你都不要自作主张，知道吗？
Don't do anything on your own from now on, okay?

11
00:01:05,080 --> 00:01:06,330
真不听话
You don't listen.

12
00:01:11,540 --> 00:01:12,630
肚子饿吗？
Are you hungry?

13
00:01:19,550 --> 00:01:20,930
你在做什么？
What are you doing?

14
00:01:23,930 --> 00:01:25,550
就这样一下子吧
Let's just stay like this.

15
00:01:40,740 --> 00:01:44,740
当我以为走到尽头的时候，我非常后悔
When I thought it was the end, I regretted it so much.

16
00:01:45,950 --> 00:01:48,950
即使给了我机会，我却还是无法坦诚
I was given another chance but wasn't honest again.

17
00:01:55,170 --> 00:01:57,210
你不会死
You won't die.

18
00:02:00,210 --> 00:02:02,420
对不起，我没能即早相信你
I'm sorry I didn't believe you.

19
00:02:10,100 --> 00:02:11,180
我更抱歉
No, I'm sorry.

20
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:19,570
吴宥拉不好对付
Yu-ra isn't an easy opponent.

21
00:02:21,530 --> 00:02:24,360
在我得知她的真面目超乎想象之后
Even after I saw her unimaginable true colors,

22
00:02:24,450 --> 00:02:26,990
还是花了超过三年的时间，才有办法和她断绝关系
it took over three years to end it with her.

23
00:02:28,740 --> 00:02:31,790
某个人超乎想象…
Someone being beyond your imagination...

24
00:02:32,540 --> 00:02:33,790
我懂那是什么意思
I know what you mean.

25
00:02:36,500 --> 00:02:38,920
跟一个人相处久了
When you spend a long time with someone,

26
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:41,260
就会看不清那个人
it's hard to see that person properly.

27
00:02:42,630 --> 00:02:45,130
心想不可能会是那样
You try not to believe it.

28
00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:50,310
都要等到看到结局才会明白
You only realize it after you see the end.

29
00:02:52,470 --> 00:02:55,390
你的前未婚妻要杀了我
Your ex-fiancée is trying to kill me,

30
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:59,190
等我死了，朴敏焕和郑秀敏就可以拿到钱
and Min-hwan and Su-min get paid if I die.

31
00:03:00,820 --> 00:03:02,480
他们携手合作了
They joined forces.

32
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:10,490
杨科长的丈夫有外遇
Ms. Yang's husband's having an affair.

33
00:03:11,950 --> 00:03:15,540
我的命运好像落到杨科长身上了
I think my fate moved to Ms. Yang.

34
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:19,130
事情不是到郑秀敏和朴敏焕结婚，就结束了
It's not over with their marriage.

35
00:03:19,210 --> 00:03:22,050
在那之后还有什么，我得找出答案
There's something more. I have to find that out.

36
00:03:22,130 --> 00:03:24,050
才能保护杨科长
To protect Ms. Yang.

37
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:29,430
你陪在我身边就好
Just stay by my side.

